Subject: Re: [VB] Only idles with choke closed

On Tue, 3 Apr 2007, John Baker wrote:

> 1500 SP bus engine will only idle when choke is closed.  Checked: No vacuum leaks, new fuel lines\filter.
>   What are other possible culprits???

OK, if it only idles with the butterfly closed you might have clogged idle
passages.  Solution is to pull the carb, take it apart, and blow out all
the passages with spray carb cleaner.  Wear eye protection.
